comments: Johnson (MIN) sets the pick in Ball's (NOP) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Holiday (NOP) and Johnson (MIN) make incidental foot contact with one another at the end of the drive.
Russell (MIN) briefly grasps Williamson (NOP) and slides his hands off after the pick.
Hernangomez (MIN) makes contact with Hart (NOP) that affects his ability to get to the rebound.
Ingram (NOP) sets the pick in Beasley's (MIN) path and absorbs the contact when contact occurs.
Johnson (MIN) is imminently exiting the lane within three seconds.
Williamson (NOP) is firming up in a picking position in Russell's (MIN) path when contact occurs, and he absorbs the contact.
Johnson (MIN) makes marginal contact with Williamson's (NOP) body during his shooting motion on the play at the basket.
Okogie (MIN) makes incidental contact with Williamson's (NOP) arm after the release on the play at the basket.
Williamson (NOP) makes some contact with Hernangomez's (MIN) arm during the rebound, but he does not prevent Hernangomez from gathering the ball.
Ingram (NOP) is not in a legal guarding position when he initiates contact with Johnson's (MIN) body during his shooting motion that affects his driving shot attempt.
Hart (NOP) places a marginal hand to Okogie's (MIN) body during his shooting motion on the play at the basket.
Russell (MIN) makes contact with Holiday's (NOP) wrist during his shooting motion that affects his jump shot attempt.
Ball (NOP) makes marginal contact with Russell (MIN) that does not affect his ability to pass.
Holiday (NOP) engages Beasley (MIN) with two hands and the contact affects his FOM.
Hart (NOP) commits a take foul on Beasley (MIN).
Johnson (MIN) and Williamson (NOP) briefly engage and separate off-ball.
Johnson (MIN) legally contests Ball's (NOP) jump shot attempt.
Holiday (NOP) commits a take foul on Russell (MIN).
Williamson (NOP) sets the screen in Okogie's (MIN) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
